## Rules
- NEVER use raw tools (Read, Write, Edit, etc.) — always use `validated_*` versions
- NEVER skip the planning step — every task needs a submitted plan
- Read files before editing them
- Follow existing code style
- Keep plans minimal — fewer steps means less that can go wrong
